Installation Instructions
=========================

Dependencies
------------

1. taglib - >= 1.7 tagging library
2. uchardet - charset detection library
3. FreeCDDB data files
4. python-docutils - rst2man required for generating manpage
5. autoconf >= 2.6 - building from source

Dependencies installation on debian:

	apt-get install g++ libuchardet-dev libtag1-dev python-docutils

FreeCDDB installation:

    wget http://ftp.freedb.org/pub/freedb/freedb-update-20120101-20120201.tar.bz2
	mkdir cddb
	cd cddb
    tar jxvf ../freedb-update-20120101-20120201.tar.bz2


Build and install
-----------------

    tar zxvf fmf-1.0.tar.gz
    cd fmf-1.0
    ./configure
    make
    make install